Homepage 

Hoast is a homeowners association web application aimed to assist with the information between the home association and the homeowners. 

Integrates Reed Solomon and AES 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ 

What is HOAST? 

With the support of Reed Solomon and AES, we aim to manage information better between the home association and the homeowners. 


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ 

Monitoring Dues is easier

With financial reports and records from HOAST, you can check on payment statuses at a glance.

Online Member Database

HOAST keep track of members information. As a result, a database including names, contact information and other crucial are maintained. It also include their roles in the community. HOAST also allow residents to access the system through a portal and update their information. 

More Security

HOAST offers a logging system for the registered vehicle of Homeowners, with the help of QR Code Generation and scanning. 

